										<div class="left-col">
																																													<p>The Clinical Center serves as a trusted source for scientific knowledge and a place where clinical research thrives.</p>

<p>Along with the clinical research training opportunities and resources that abound at the Clinical Center there is a rich reservoir of information and assistance for physicians and healthcare professionals.</p>

											                      										</div>
									</aside>
								
																	<!-- BOTH Sidebars -->
									<div class="col-sm-12 col-md-6 content-area">
																																	    <h1 class="page-header"><span property="schema:name">For Researchers and Physicians</span>
</h1>


																															  <article data-history-node-id="45425" role="article" about="/researchers1.html" typeof="schema:WebPage" class="page full clearfix">

  
      <span property="schema:name" content="For Researchers and Physicians" class="hidden"></span>


  
  <div class="content">
    
            <div property="schema:text" class="field field--name-body field--type-text-with-summary field--label-hidden field--item"><p><a href="https://ocr.od.nih.gov/" title="Curriculum in Clinical Research"><strong>Curriculum in Clinical Research</strong></a><br />
Courses, degree programs and more.</p>

<p><a href="https://ocr.od.nih.gov/funding_opportunities.html" title="Collaborating with NIH Intramural Investigators"><strong>Collaborating with NIH Intramural Investigators</strong></a><br />
Special resources at the NIH, opportunities for research collaborations.</p>

<p><a href="referpatients/index.html" title="Information for Referring Physicians"><strong>Information for Referring Physicians</strong></a><br />
Search the Studies, contact information, how to refer a patient and more.</p>

<p><a href="researchers/lectures.shtml" title="Lectures"><strong>Lectures</strong></a><br />
Current and archived lecture series include Grand Rounds, Astute Clinicians and more.</p>

<p><a href="/ocmr/research-discoveries.html" title="Medical Milestones &amp; Clinical Center Firsts"><strong>Medical Milestones &amp; Clinical Center Firsts</strong></a><br />
Highlights of scientific discoveries made at the NIH Clinical Center.</p>

<p><a href="/meet-our-doctors/index.html" title="Meet Our Doctors"><strong>Meet Our Doctors</strong></a><br />
Clinician information.</p>

<p><a href="http://intranet.cc.nih.gov/recruit/opr.html" title="NIH Intramural Investigators Looking to Recruit Patients/Healthy Volunteers (NIH Staff Only)"><strong>NIH Intramural Investigators Looking to Recruit Patients/Healthy Volunteers (NIH Staff Only)</strong></a><br />
Need to reach more patients for your study? The NIH Clinical Center Office of Patient Recruitment offers free services to all NIH intramural researchers needing to enroll patients and healthy volunteers. The office provides strategic recruitment campaigns that include social media marketing, public service announcements, posters, and community outreach initiatives.</p>

<p><strong><a href="/ocmr/abstracts/index.html" title="Research at the NIH Clinical Center">Research at the NIH Clinical Center</a></strong><br />
Here is a sample of abstracts from the clinical research conducted at the NIH Clinical Center and published in a peer reviewed medical journal this year. Links to the full text and video formats are provided if available.</p>

<p><a href="researchers/resources.html" title="Resources for Researchers"><strong>Resources for Researchers</strong></a><br />
Bench-to-Bedside awards, Biomedical Translational Research Information System (BTRIS), Clinical Research Standards, and more.</p>

<p><a href="about/SeniorStaff/index.html" title="Senior Staff"><strong>Senior Staff</strong></a><br />
Contact information.<br />
<br />
<a href="/training/index.html" title="Training Programs and Continuing Medical Education"><strong>Training Programs and Continuing Medical Education</strong></a><br />
Fellowships, residency programs internships, and more.</p>
</div>
      
  </div>

</article>


